    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      154.93,
      519.21,
      195.81
    ],
    "text": "Investigations have been initiated at the Omantha Police Station following a report that a person was fatally attacked with a sharp-edged weapon in the Navatkulam area of the Omantha Police Division on the night of 06.06.2026.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      210.37,
      422.5,
      223.65
    ],
    "text": "The deceased is a 32-year-old resident of Navatkulam, Omantha.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      238.12,
      524.55,
      279.0
    ],
    "text": "Preliminary inquiries indicate that a suspect within a group assaulted the victim with a sharp object while intervening in a dispute that had arisen near the Navatkulam Kovil between the victim\u2019s mother and a group of relatives.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      293.56,
      525.39,
      320.64
    ],
    "text": "The body has been placed at the Vavuniya Hospital mortuary, and Omantha Police are conducting investigations to apprehend the suspect.",
