      737.99,
      518.52,
      778.75
    ],
    "text": "Investigations have been initiated at the Hikkaduwa Police Station following a report received on the evening of 06.06.2026 that a body had been discovered on Kumarakanda Beach within the Hikkaduwa Police Division.",
