      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      31.91,
      523.59,
      86.61
    ],
    "text": "On 06.06.2026, Jayapuram Police have launched investigations following a complaint received on 05.06.2026 regarding a staff member of the Jayapuram Forest Office within the Jayapuram Police Division, who had been reported missing since the same date.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      101.17,
      519.37,
      155.85
    ],
    "text": "During search operations carried out by investigating officers with the assistance of a police dog unit, the missing person\u2019s mobile phone was discovered behind the forest office premises. Subsequently, upon inspection of a nearby well, the body of the missing individual was recovered.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      170.41,
      402.43,
      183.69
    ],
    "text": "The deceased was a 41-year-old resident of Thambuttegama.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      198.13,
      505.95,
      225.21
    ],
    "text": "The body remains under police custody at the scene for a magisterial examination, while Jayapuram Police continue further investigations.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
